nodes.text: Kaminoan KE-8 Enforcer: An Expanded Universe Ship

Kaminoan KE-8 Enforcer: An Expanded Universe Ship is a web enhancement written by Cory J. Herndon and released by Wizards of the Coast on April 10, 2003 as a companion to Inside the Worlds of Star Wars: Attack of the Clones. It provides a description and Star Wars Roleplaying Game stats for the KE-8 Enforcer.
